SecureSocial,is,a,cloud,based,social,and,global,identity,platform,that,focuses,on,security,and,privacy,for,its,users,Message,and,document,content,is,secure,even,from,service,operators,SecureSocial,Identities,are,represented,by,a,public,key,and,an,encrypted,private,key,to,securely,identify,users,The,SecureSocial,API,allows,applications,to,manage,identities,content,and,messages,The,API,accepts,HTTP,calls,and,authenticates,using,an,encryption,process,built,around,a,SHA,hash,and,a,user,s,SecureSocial,private,key